    <h2>14. Governing Law; Dispute Resolution</h2>
    <p>This Agreement is governed by the laws of {{governing_law_state}}, without regard to conflicts principles. Disputes shall be resolved by {{dispute_forum}} (e.g., binding arbitration under AAA rules) seated in {{dispute_venue_city}}, except that the Company may seek injunctive relief in any court of competent jurisdiction.</p>

    <h2>15. Miscellaneous</h2>
    <ul>
