      <li><strong>Amendments.</strong> Must be in a signed writing.</li>
      <li><strong>Assignment.</strong> Company may assign; Contributor may not assign without Company consent.</li>
      <li><strong>Severability.</strong> If any provision is invalid, the remainder remains effective.</li>
      <li><strong>Counterparts; E-Signatures.</strong> Executable in counterparts; electronic signatures are valid.</li>
    </ul>

